<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ARES - Sito Ufficiale</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #DFBD69; /* Oro */
      --secondary-color: #000000; /* Nero */
      --text-color: #FFFFFF; /* Bianco */
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      color: var(--text-color);
    }

    header {
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    nav a {
      color: var(--text-color);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), var(--secondary-color)), url('images/GameIcon2.png') center/cover no-repeat;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .download-buttons {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .download-buttons a {
      background-color: var(--primary-color);
      color: var(--secondary-color);
      padding: 15px 30px;
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .download-buttons a:hover {
      background-color: #b9954c; /* Oro più scuro */
    }

    .info-section {
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      padding: 50px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .info-section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    .info-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: var(--secondary-color);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--primary-color);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: #b9954c;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="logo">ARES</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#">Home</a>
      <a href="#info">Informazioni</a>
      <a href="#download">Download</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contatti</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Benvenuto in ARES</h1>
    <p>Scopri il futuro del gaming multiplayer. Esplora, personalizza, combatti e domina in un universo futuristico con una grafica mozzafiato.</p>
    <div class="download-buttons" id="download">
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=macOS-file-id">Scarica per MacOS</a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=windows-file-id">Scarica per Windows</a>
      <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/">Disponibile su Steam</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="info-section" id="info">
    <h2>Informazioni sul Gioco</h2>
    <p><strong>Sviluppatore:</strong> Cristiano Rotunno</p>
    <p><strong>Data di Uscita:</strong> 2025</p>
    <p><strong>Piattaforme:</strong> Windows, MacOS</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2025 ARES. Tutti i diritti riservati.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
